@startuml
title UML State Machine Diagram

state Initial
state LoggedIn
state JourneyDetails
state DrivingMode
state Hungry
state RestaurantSelection
state Ordering
state AccidentReport
state Notifications
state Feedback
state Logout

[*] --> Initial : Initialize

Initial --> LoggedIn : Login

LoggedIn --> JourneyDetails : Select destination

JourneyDetails : entry / Display journey details
JourneyDetails : do / Show options
JourneyDetails --> DrivingMode : Activate driving mode
JourneyDetails --> JourneyDetails : Choose other options
JourneyDetails --> Hungry : Select eat

DrivingMode : entry / Activate
DrivingMode : do / Monitor
DrivingMode --> JourneyDetails : Deactivate
DrivingMode --> AccidentReport : Accident detected

Hungry --> RestaurantSelection : Select place

RestaurantSelection : entry / Display menu
RestaurantSelection --> Ordering : Order

Ordering : entry / Place order
Ordering --> JourneyDetails : Continue journey
Ordering --> Notifications : Order confirmed

AccidentReport --> Notifications : Report accident

Notifications : entry / Send notifications
Notifications --> JourneyDetails : Continue
Notifications --> DrivingMode : Continue driving
Notifications --> Feedback : Provide feedback

Feedback --> Logout : Submit

Logout --> [*] : Logout complete
@enduml
